query:
WITH
       pf AS (
             INSERT INTO profile_feeds (id, profile_id, feed_id)
             VALUES ($1, $2, $3)
                 ON CONFLICT (profile_id, feed_id) DO NOTHING
          RETURNING id
       )
SELECT id AS "id!"
  FROM pf
 UNION ALL
SELECT id
  FROM profile_feeds
 WHERE profile_id = $2
   AND feed_id = $3
